title: 'Scratch and dent in the medium size box'
body: 'I noticed some scratches and a dent in the middle size. Large and cabin size items are good. But disappointed with the middle size. Issue not with the product but with the mode of delivery. The delivery boy brought the huge box tied in a bike and handled roughly during unloading from the vehicle. I was in USA where the huge items are transport and delivered using a van. But here in India most of the items are delivered via motorcycle or scooter irrespective of thier size and weight.'
